Source Code to Image

Installation

go get github.com/nayzawoo/ss

Usage

NAME:
   Code Screenshot - ss <options> [sourcecode]

USAGE:
   ss [global options] command [command options] [arguments...]

VERSION:
   0.0.0

COMMANDS:
     help, h  Shows a list of commands or help for one command

GLOBAL OPTIONS:
   --lang LANGUAGE, -l LANGUAGE  LANGUAGE (default: "auto")
   --output FILE, -o FILE        Output FILE (default: "home")
   --style STYLE, -s STYLE       Theme STYLE (default: "monokai")
   --help, -h                    show help
   --version, -v                 print the version


Available Styles: https://github.com/alecthomas/chroma/tree/master/styles
Available Languages: https://github.com/alecthomas/chroma/tree/master/lexers


```
ss -o ./example.png -s vim -l jsx dummy/code.jsx
```

